title: The Ticket’s Not Free
author: VD
content_html:
Oprah Winfrey: You’re going to be such a big star, Rita!

Rita Ora: Ohmigosh, that’s wonderful, Oprah. Thank you so much for believing in me!

Oprah Winfrey: Oh, I do, honey. You’ve got what it takes. Now, have you met my friend Harvey?
